{"_id":"N0jI41Iw8sOmqxMh","name":"Alice of Other Worlds - Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I am a young doctor who has dedicated her whole life to the treatment of mental illnesses. I understand \nthem, for I am suffering from one as well, and only those who burned themselves while playing with \nfire can understand its dangers. After a dark period during which I managed a sanatorium, the Order \nstripped me of all academic honors and degrees, reducing me to the status of a criminal. But it didn’t \ntake long for them to understand the extent of my studies and the magnitude of my abilities. After \npossessing the Pope himself, I struck a deal with the Order. They will allow me to continue my studies, \nbut I may only study the creatures they fight. And perhaps, through the distorted minds of the Broken \nTales, I can prove that the worlds I visited as a child are real and not the ramblings of a mad mind.","notes":"Alice of Other Worlds - bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 2.","positive":"I am a young doctor who has dedicated her whole life to the treatment of mental illnesses. I understand them, for I am suffering from one as well, and only those who burned themselves while playing with fire can understand its dangers. After a dark period during which I managed a sanatorium, the Order stripped me of all academic honors and degrees, reducing me to the status of a criminal. But it didn’t take long for them to understand the extent of my studies and the magnitude of my abilities. After possessing the Pope himself, I struck a deal with the Order. They will allow me to continue my studies, but I may only study the creatures they fight. And perhaps, through the distorted minds of the Broken Tales, I can prove that the worlds I visited as a child are real and not the ramblings of a mad mind.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"category":"Broken One Descriptor"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783968469028,"modifiedTime":1783968469028,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"bqC08oE8Zcvhj8aO","name":"Alice of Other Worlds - Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I am a skilled physician and psychiatrist, and \ndiagnosing illnesses is simple. My work has made me \nparticularly cold and detached.","notes":"Alice of Other Worlds - bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 2.","positive":"I am a skilled physician and psychiatrist, and diagnosing illnesses is simple. My work has made me particularly cold and detached.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"category":"Broken One Descriptor"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783968469028,"modifiedTime":1783968469028,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"kwuAeebBaxf4PZ6L","name":"Alice of Other Worlds - Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Cheshire, my faithful trained lynx, is the most \ntrustworthy of companions – a shadow keeping \nme safe from threats. Cheshire’s attachment is an \nobsession and she may even threaten those who don’t \nwant to hurt me.","notes":"Alice of Other Worlds - bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 2.","positive":"Cheshire, my faithful trained lynx, is the most trustworthy of companions – a shadow keeping me safe from threats. Cheshire’s attachment is an obsession and she may even threaten those who don’t want to hurt me.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"category":"Broken One Descriptor"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783968469028,"modifiedTime":1783968469028,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"vm1peVHYUeLqHu7h","name":"Alice of Other Worlds - Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Alice of\nOther Worlds\nAs a child I traveled to other worlds and my mind can perceive and see \nthings beyond common perception. Memories of my childhood haunt me, \nand I often get lost in visions of the past.","notes":"Alice of Other Worlds - bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 2.","positive":"Alice of Other Worlds As a child I traveled to other worlds and my mind can perceive and see things beyond common perception. Memories of my childhood haunt me, and I often get lost in visions of the past.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"category":"Broken One Descriptor"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783968469028,"modifiedTime":1783968469028,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"6O46HXGevpro2MEe","name":"Beauty and her Beast - Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I am Bellina Cantalupo, but everyone calls me Bella. I was once a servant to the bride of the monstrous Dionysus \nGonsalva. I played my cards well, charmed the nobleman, and rose to power. Unfortunately, the Order got in the \nway and sabotaged everything I had built. As a punishment, I was magically bound to Dionysus and now our \nsouls are intertwined. I feel his pain and his beastly instincts. Dionysus perceives, in turn, my disgust for him, \nbut it doesn’t affect the mad love he feels for me. I serve the Order in the hope of gaining its grace and being \nreleased from this punishment. But, deep down in my heart, I still long for the power that I was denied being born \na peasant, but that I know I deserve.","notes":"Beauty and her Beast - bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 4.","positive":"I am Bellina Cantalupo, but everyone calls me Bella. I was once a servant to the bride of the monstrous Dionysus Gonsalva. I played my cards well, charmed the nobleman, and rose to power. Unfortunately, the Order got in the way and sabotaged everything I had built. As a punishment, I was magically bound to Dionysus and now our souls are intertwined. I feel his pain and his beastly instincts. Dionysus perceives, in turn, my disgust for him, but it doesn’t affect the mad love he feels for me. I serve the Order in the hope of gaining its grace and being released from this punishment. But, deep down in my heart, I still long for the power that I was denied being born a peasant, but that I know I deserve.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"category":"Broken One Descriptor"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783968469028,"modifiedTime":1783968469028,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"07QDJ5XstMDU9AIl","name":"Beauty and her Beast - Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Dionysus follows me and protects me like a faithful beast, \nand responds to all my commands. As useful as this is, I feel \ndisgusted every time he comes near me.","notes":"Beauty and her Beast - bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 4.","positive":"Dionysus follows me and protects me like a faithful beast, and responds to all my commands. As useful as this is, I feel disgusted every time he comes near me.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"category":"Broken One Descriptor"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783968469028,"modifiedTime":1783968469028,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"eX7JYFDRXHzVfQBP","name":"Beauty and her Beast - Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I am charismatic and affable. My innate air of superiority \nfascinates simple people. I love having all my eyes on me.","notes":"Beauty and her Beast - bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 4.","positive":"I am charismatic and affable. My innate air of superiority fascinates simple people. I love having all my eyes on me.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"category":"Broken One Descriptor"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783968469028,"modifiedTime":1783968469028,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"6lJtzEGBJOF47K2x","name":"Beauty and her Beast - Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I am linked to Dionysus and we share pain and perceptions. He will \nalways know where I am and vice versa. For me, that’s the most \nhumiliating part of the curse.","notes":"Beauty and her Beast - bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 4.","positive":"I am linked to Dionysus and we share pain and perceptions. He will always know where I am and vice versa. For me, that’s the most humiliating part of the curse.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"category":"Broken One Descriptor"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783968469028,"modifiedTime":1783968469028,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"mVUjm59bivfSWScr","name":"Bloodwhite - Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I am a mutant and can alter my body as I wish. The Order uses \nmy unique abilities to support other Hunters. When it changes, \nmy body emits a particular hormone that arouses those close \nto me.","notes":"Bloodwhite - bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 6.","positive":"I am a mutant and can alter my body as I wish. The Order uses my unique abilities to support other Hunters. When it changes, my body emits a particular hormone that arouses those close to me.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"category":"Broken One Descriptor"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783968469028,"modifiedTime":1783968469028,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"P4o3mflPjsmlLeIf","name":"Bloodwhite - Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"My touch is capable of mutating other beings with devastating \nresults. The flesh deforms before it explodes. When I am in the \ngrip of strong emotions, I lose control of my power and I am \nafraid to touch the people I care about.","notes":"Bloodwhite - bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 6.","positive":"My touch is capable of mutating other beings with devastating results. The flesh deforms before it explodes. When I am in the grip of strong emotions, I lose control of my power and I am afraid to touch the people I care about.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"category":"Broken One Descriptor"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783968469028,"modifiedTime":1783968469028,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"ztKkpD58mLRZmzaG","name":"Bloodwhite - Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I am a good girl and believe in the power of love and justice. My \npure gaze reaches the hearts of the people close to me. I try to \navoid those that look at me with disgust, believing me to be a \nmonster.","notes":"Bloodwhite - bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 6.","positive":"I am a good girl and believe in the power of love and justice. My pure gaze reaches the hearts of the people close to me. I try to avoid those that look at me with disgust, believing me to be a monster.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"category":"Broken One Descriptor"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783968469028,"modifiedTime":1783968469028,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"9Y31BE06NAVsP1GR","name":"Wound. Carlo the LivingPuppet - Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"My life is animated by the magic of lies, and for this reason \nI am skilled at recognizing and using both falsehoods and \nmagic. Even if admitting it is hurtful, my own life is a lie and \nI move only because I pretend to be a real child.","notes":"Wound. Carlo the LivingPuppet - bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 8.","positive":"My life is animated by the magic of lies, and for this reason I am skilled at recognizing and using both falsehoods and magic. Even if admitting it is hurtful, my own life is a lie and I move only because I pretend to be a real child.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"category":"Broken One Descriptor"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783968469028,"modifiedTime":1783968469028,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"lpLFYPa5jcF6g7GX","name":"Wound. Carlo the LivingPuppet - Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I want to prove that I am a good boy, and that is why I strive \nto perform every task that is assigned to me. I naively tend to \ntrust adults blindly, even if I just met them.","notes":"Wound. Carlo the LivingPuppet - bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 8.","positive":"I want to prove that I am a good boy, and that is why I strive to perform every task that is assigned to me. I naively tend to trust adults blindly, even if I just met them.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"category":"Broken One Descriptor"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783968469029,"modifiedTime":1783968469029,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"VOZGxvDPbAyQEiLH","name":"Hatta Carter - Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I am obsessed with time and when I can plan an action out, I can \ncomplete it half the time a normal person would need. Sometimes \nI lose focus on what I am doing, using twice as much time to \ncomplete the simplest actions.","notes":"Hatta Carter - bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 10.","positive":"I am obsessed with time and when I can plan an action out, I can complete it half the time a normal person would need. Sometimes I lose focus on what I am doing, using twice as much time to complete the simplest actions.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"category":"Broken One Descriptor"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783968469029,"modifiedTime":1783968469029,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"z6MhHERQSLuVgO0W","name":"Hatta Carter - Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I am a good toymaker and the small automata I build can \nperform the most varied tasks. All my creations have a touch \nof my madness and sometimes they don’t work exactly as they \nshould.","notes":"Hatta Carter - bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 10.","positive":"I am a good toymaker and the small automata I build can perform the most varied tasks. All my creations have a touch of my madness and sometimes they don’t work exactly as they should.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"category":"Broken One Descriptor"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783968469029,"modifiedTime":1783968469029,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"Qm6tL90SQzh0ae9w","name":"The Knight with a Hundred Heads - Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I am a swordsman and a Hussar knight with finely honed \ncombat skills. Ordog is more than a common horse and he \noften saved me with his magic. Sometimes I wonder who the \nreal Hunter of the Order is.","notes":"The Knight with a Hundred Heads - bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 12.","positive":"I am a swordsman and a Hussar knight with finely honed combat skills. Ordog is more than a common horse and he often saved me with his magic. Sometimes I wonder who the real Hunter of the Order is.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"category":"Broken One Descriptor"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783968469029,"modifiedTime":1783968469029,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"M3BV3I8O5PNAQA66","name":"The Knight with a Hundred Heads - Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I am a tenacious defender and in my previous life, I always \nstood my ground, never retreating. The memory of my loved \nones makes me melancholic and I cannot forgive those who \nhurt families.","notes":"The Knight with a Hundred Heads - bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 12.","positive":"I am a tenacious defender and in my previous life, I always stood my ground, never retreating. The memory of my loved ones makes me melancholic and I cannot forgive those who hurt families.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"category":"Broken One Descriptor"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783968469029,"modifiedTime":1783968469029,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"fxVl40o5uuU1kElR","name":"Iskra the Young Wolf - Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"After another year of education and training, I finally found in the Order my new pack and made the \nHunters my trusted hunting companions. I serve the Order with strength and dedication, happy to do \neverything the alpha Hunter asks of me.","notes":"Iskra the Young Wolf - bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 14.","positive":"After another year of education and training, I finally found in the Order my new pack and made the Hunters my trusted hunting companions. I serve the Order with strength and dedication, happy to do everything the alpha Hunter asks of me.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"category":"Broken One Descriptor"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783968469029,"modifiedTime":1783968469029,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"vvc3jyNdj0bymArT","name":"Iskra the Young Wolf - Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"When I am calm, I still look like a small and helpless child \nand, thanks to this, adults tend to underestimate me. I struggle to \nbehave like a normal child, but I can’t keep my wolfish side leashed \nforever.","notes":"Iskra the Young Wolf - bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 14.","positive":"When I am calm, I still look like a small and helpless child and, thanks to this, adults tend to underestimate me. I struggle to behave like a normal child, but I can’t keep my wolfish side leashed forever.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"category":"Broken One Descriptor"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783968469029,"modifiedTime":1783968469029,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"wXcGYHjQQM8zc2Ht","name":"Iskra the Young Wolf - Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I perform my best when I’m cooperating with my hunting \ncompanions. I quickly learn the strengths and weaknesses of the \npack. I follow every order of anyone I consider more important \nthan me within the pack, without hesitation or remorse.","notes":"Iskra the Young Wolf - bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 14.","positive":"I perform my best when I’m cooperating with my hunting companions. I quickly learn the strengths and weaknesses of the pack. I follow every order of anyone I consider more important than me within the pack, without hesitation or remorse.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"category":"Broken One Descriptor"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783968469029,"modifiedTime":1783968469029,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"K9OlkzLSozQatsGY","name":"Iskra the Young Wolf - Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Iskra the\n Young\nWolf I am a wolf child and I defend myself with fangs and claws. My \nsense of smell is infallible. I’m young and I know little about the \nworld, so I am easily intimidated when I face something I don’t \nknow.","notes":"Iskra the Young Wolf - bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 14.","positive":"Iskra the Young Wolf I am a wolf child and I defend myself with fangs and claws. My sense of smell is infallible. I’m young and I know little about the world, so I am easily intimidated when I face something I don’t know.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"category":"Broken One Descriptor"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783968469029,"modifiedTime":1783968469029,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"R4EQULDxHlwqSdwz","name":"The Gang of three Pigs - Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"We are three brothers who renounced their names to become emissaries of the God Under the Mine. We \nwere a group of anarchists and rebels, but the Order captured us, forcing us to become Hunters. We carry with \nus the last piece of the God Under the Mine, an ancient and powerful creature. We keep the remains of the God a \nsecret so that the Order won’t get their grubby hands on it. By feeding on it, our bodies can regenerate and even \nreturn from death, effectively making our gang immortal.","notes":"The Gang of three Pigs - bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 16.","positive":"We are three brothers who renounced their names to become emissaries of the God Under the Mine. We were a group of anarchists and rebels, but the Order captured us, forcing us to become Hunters. We carry with us the last piece of the God Under the Mine, an ancient and powerful creature. We keep the remains of the God a secret so that the Order won’t get their grubby hands on it. By feeding on it, our bodies can regenerate and even return from death, effectively making our gang immortal.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"category":"Broken One Descriptor"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783968469029,"modifiedTime":1783968469029,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"6UMiYUngsZUn0uwP","name":"The Gang of three Pigs - Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"We are a gang and we use numerical superiority \nto overcome our human limitations. Our faces \nare always covered by a pig’s head mask, \nintimidating ordinary people.","notes":"The Gang of three Pigs - bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 16.","positive":"We are a gang and we use numerical superiority to overcome our human limitations. Our faces are always covered by a pig’s head mask, intimidating ordinary people.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"category":"Broken One Descriptor"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783968469029,"modifiedTime":1783968469029,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"uzluPKdcRJv1WBNY","name":"The Gang of three Pigs - Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Thanks to the flesh of the God Under the Mine, \nour body is able to regenerate. We do not fear \npain or disease. Preserving the God’s meat is an \nobsession for us, and is more important than \nanything else.","notes":"The Gang of three Pigs - bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 16.","positive":"Thanks to the flesh of the God Under the Mine, our body is able to regenerate. We do not fear pain or disease. Preserving the God’s meat is an obsession for us, and is more important than anything else.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"category":"Broken One Descriptor"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783968469029,"modifiedTime":1783968469029,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"hFVW7b0xx0N3rgpc","name":"The Gang of three Pigs - Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"We are capable builders and there is no building that we cannot fortify or infiltrate. We \nare very protective of what we think is ours.","notes":"The Gang of three Pigs - bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 16.","positive":"We are capable builders and there is no building that we cannot fortify or infiltrate. We are very protective of what we think is ours.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"category":"Broken One Descriptor"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783968469029,"modifiedTime":1783968469029,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"1D52Ulxq6gAfUHYD","name":"Morgana of the Lake - Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I have always had an intuitive understanding of destiny. \nDreams and visions may come over me uncontrollably, giving \nme a glimpse of the right thread to follow. I often see things \nI’ d rather not and live with the pain of finding out what will \nhappen in the future of someone I care about.","notes":"Morgana of the Lake - bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 18.","positive":"I have always had an intuitive understanding of destiny. Dreams and visions may come over me uncontrollably, giving me a glimpse of the right thread to follow. I often see things I’ d rather not and live with the pain of finding out what will happen in the future of someone I care about.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"category":"Broken One Descriptor"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783968469029,"modifiedTime":1783968469029,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"XobLohu8YRF3A5bd","name":"Morgana of the Lake - Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I am a skilled illusionist. Thanks to my power, I can conjure \ntricks of light and mirages. I am hopelessly attracted to mirrors \nand sleights of hand.","notes":"Morgana of the Lake - bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 18.","positive":"I am a skilled illusionist. Thanks to my power, I can conjure tricks of light and mirages. I am hopelessly attracted to mirrors and sleights of hand.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"category":"Broken One Descriptor"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783968469029,"modifiedTime":1783968469029,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"Ef6c5j3dZH6RWLAe","name":"OZena the Suffering - Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Even if sometimes the memories of my “past in the future” resurface, making me homesick... What if the Order \nis deceiving me as Henkle did? Am I always meant to be just a pawn in someone else’s game?","notes":"OZena the Suffering - bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 20.","positive":"Even if sometimes the memories of my “past in the future” resurface, making me homesick... What if the Order is deceiving me as Henkle did? Am I always meant to be just a pawn in someone else’s game?","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"category":"Broken One Descriptor"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783968469029,"modifiedTime":1783968469029,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"b197a1nhKEJlsuWZ","name":"OZena the Suffering - Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I trained to be an efficient fighter and assassin, taking \nadvantage of the magical shoes I took from my first \nvictim. The disease that afflicts me disfigures my face and I \nam ashamed of my condition.","notes":"OZena the Suffering - bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 20.","positive":"I trained to be an efficient fighter and assassin, taking advantage of the magical shoes I took from my first victim. The disease that afflicts me disfigures my face and I am ashamed of my condition.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"category":"Broken One Descriptor"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783968469029,"modifiedTime":1783968469029,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"9LPpmTwd9CpZ8lrE","name":"OZena the Suffering - Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I have been leading a band of followers for a long time and I \nknow how a leader should behave. I’m good at imposing my \nwill on others. Even though I am often offered loyalty, being \na stranger far from my home in time and space makes it \ndifficult to trust others.","notes":"OZena the Suffering - bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 20.","positive":"I have been leading a band of followers for a long time and I know how a leader should behave. I’m good at imposing my will on others. Even though I am often offered loyalty, being a stranger far from my home in time and space makes it difficult to trust others.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"category":"Broken One Descriptor"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783968469030,"modifiedTime":1783968469030,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"bSxuhePgNYyYnPwK","name":"OZena the Suffering - Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I am a person out of her time and largely immune to those who use spells and \nmagic. I have a natural talent for fighting those who use magic. I hate witches \nand sorcerers because, despite their power, they can’t heal me.","notes":"OZena the Suffering - bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 20.","positive":"I am a person out of her time and largely immune to those who use spells and magic. I have a natural talent for fighting those who use magic. I hate witches and sorcerers because, despite their power, they can’t heal me.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"category":"Broken One Descriptor"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783968469030,"modifiedTime":1783968469030,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"CaoZ3ErkElq25s8G","name":"Sherazade the Weaver of Tales - Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I hate violence in all its forms and all I wish to do is brighten people’s hearts through stories \nand poems.","notes":"Sherazade the Weaver of Tales - bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 22.","positive":"I hate violence in all its forms and all I wish to do is brighten people’s hearts through stories and poems.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"category":"Broken One Descriptor"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783968469030,"modifiedTime":1783968469030,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"PgoJ2uuMk6MPT07B","name":"Sherazade the Weaver of Tales - Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I know over a thousand stories and from each one I draw \na lesson with which to face dangers. I’ d do anything to \nlearn a new story.","notes":"Sherazade the Weaver of Tales - bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 22.","positive":"I know over a thousand stories and from each one I draw a lesson with which to face dangers. I’ d do anything to learn a new story.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"category":"Broken One Descriptor"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783968469030,"modifiedTime":1783968469030,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"JBy8zQbzQTUlLghl","name":"Sherazade the Weaver of Tales - Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I know the delicate art of flattery and I know how to best \ncompliment others to make them feel good. I will not \ntolerate those who use violence.","notes":"Sherazade the Weaver of Tales - bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 22.","positive":"I know the delicate art of flattery and I know how to best compliment others to make them feel good. I will not tolerate those who use violence.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"category":"Broken One Descriptor"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783968469030,"modifiedTime":1783968469030,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"uMJHvyJRYNWgn8MZ","name":"Sherazade the Weaver of Tales - Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"Sherazade \nthe Weaver of \nTales\nMy stories become reality. Shadows, those ubiquitous reflections of \nreality, can interact with me. A life among the shadows in my bedroom \nhas made it hard for me to bear sunlight.","notes":"Sherazade the Weaver of Tales - bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 22.","positive":"Sherazade the Weaver of Tales My stories become reality. Shadows, those ubiquitous reflections of reality, can interact with me. A life among the shadows in my bedroom has made it hard for me to bear sunlight.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"category":"Broken One Descriptor"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783968469030,"modifiedTime":1783968469030,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"uqxQ9hlJn0l2plDX","name":"Talia the Sleeper - Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I am a cursed daughter, born from a forbidden love, destined to sleep forever. However, \nmy mind is alert and I perceive what is happening in the world around me. The curse that \nafflicts me allows me to manipulate objects, which is why the Order kept me alive after saving \nme from the castle that was my home and prison. As a Hunter, I am committed to ending \ninjustice and I hope to find a cure for my curse. However, the only thing I truly wish to find is \nsomeone who won’t break my heart.","notes":"Talia the Sleeper - bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 24.","positive":"I am a cursed daughter, born from a forbidden love, destined to sleep forever. However, my mind is alert and I perceive what is happening in the world around me. The curse that afflicts me allows me to manipulate objects, which is why the Order kept me alive after saving me from the castle that was my home and prison. As a Hunter, I am committed to ending injustice and I hope to find a cure for my curse. However, the only thing I truly wish to find is someone who won’t break my heart.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"category":"Broken One Descriptor"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783968469030,"modifiedTime":1783968469030,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"FfiPn8Bkmicb59qD","name":"Talia the Sleeper - Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"My body floats, carried by my power, ignoring obstacles of all \nkinds. I can use my very long hair as if it were my hands. I \ntravel in a heavy nun’s habit and wear a mask to hide my true \ncondition from the world.","notes":"Talia the Sleeper - bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 24.","positive":"My body floats, carried by my power, ignoring obstacles of all kinds. I can use my very long hair as if it were my hands. I travel in a heavy nun’s habit and wear a mask to hide my true condition from the world.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"category":"Broken One Descriptor"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783968469030,"modifiedTime":1783968469030,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"8a56CXkH1YDR5EbN","name":"Talia the Sleeper - Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I can communicate with those who are asleep or \nunderstand their desires and fears through dreams. I hate \nit when there are too many people around. The buzz of their \nlives reminds me of what I can’t have.","notes":"Talia the Sleeper - bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 24.","positive":"I can communicate with those who are asleep or understand their desires and fears through dreams. I hate it when there are too many people around. The buzz of their lives reminds me of what I can’t have.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"category":"Broken One Descriptor"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783968469030,"modifiedTime":1783968469030,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"9sFEIj75SdxmCUkR","name":"Talia the Sleeper - Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I can move objects with the power of thought alone. Through this power, \nI am able to manifest my presence in the world. My real body is immobile \nand locked in eternal sleep, at the mercy of the world. I long for the \nleast caress, which would remind me of being alive.","notes":"Talia the Sleeper - bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 24.","positive":"I can move objects with the power of thought alone. Through this power, I am able to manifest my presence in the world. My real body is immobile and locked in eternal sleep, at the mercy of the world. I long for the least caress, which would remind me of being alive.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"category":"Broken One Descriptor"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783968469030,"modifiedTime":1783968469030,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"qdNLVAtHb3WwktuA","name":"Yvonne of the Dark - Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I died with my beloved candles in my hand and \nwas reborn with the power to control fire. I hate \nstaying in the darkness and I always want at least \na small source of light.","notes":"Yvonne of the Dark - bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 26.","positive":"I died with my beloved candles in my hand and was reborn with the power to control fire. I hate staying in the darkness and I always want at least a small source of light.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"category":"Broken One Descriptor"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783968469030,"modifiedTime":1783968469030,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"Ywjsd16Ork0zjhWk","name":"Yvonne of the Dark - Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"I have no choice but to remain in my childish \nbody for eternity. I have a sweet smile and \npeople often feel protective towards me. Animals \nperceive me for who I really am and they act up \nin my presence.","notes":"Yvonne of the Dark - bt-tbo-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-14].pdf, pages 26.","positive":"I have no choice but to remain in my childish body for eternity. I have a sweet smile and people often feel protective towards me. Animals perceive me for who I really am and they act up in my presence.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"category":"Broken One Descriptor"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783968469030,"modifiedTime":1783968469030,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
